@startuml fault_handling_etcd_degradation
hide empty description
skinparam shadowing false

title 第三方：etcd 故障模式与 KVC 行为（概要）

state "etcd 集群正常\n(HA)" as Normal
state "单节点 etcd 故障" as Single
state "续租失败 / 单链路" as Lease
state "全部 etcd 不可用" as AllDown

[*] --> Normal

Normal : 无额外影响
Single : 集群容错，通常无影响
Lease : 触发故障隔离\n（见 fault_handling_sdk_etcd_failover）
AllDown : 降级：缓存集群视图；\n数据面在方案前提下可保持；\n扩缩容/隔离受影响

Normal --> Single : 单副本故障
Normal --> Lease : 网络分区等
Normal --> AllDown : 灾难场景

Single --> Normal : 恢复
Lease --> Normal : 恢复
AllDown --> Normal : etcd 恢复

note bottom of AllDown
  与 FAULT_HANDLING §四 表一致；以现网版本为准
end note

@enduml
